    <title>IEEE TNNLS | EmT：一种用于广义跨被试EEG情绪识别的新型Transformer模型</title>
    <link href="https://aisakaaoi.github.io/ddd74882.html"/>
    <id>https://aisakaaoi.github.io/ddd74882.html</id>
    <published>2026-01-05T18:58:03.000Z</published>
